## ğŸ“š Topics Covered:
- Learned the 4 core REST API operations:
  - `GET` â†’ Retrieve data
  - `POST` â†’ Create new data
  - `PUT` â†’ Update existing data
  - `DELETE` â†’ Remove data
- Created dummy endpoints in Spring Boot
